Arthroscopic Treatment of Concurrent Avulsion Fracture of Anterior and Posterior 
Cruciate Ligament with Suspension Device.

Lombardo-Torre M(1), Espejo-Reina A(2), García-Gutiérrez G(3), Espejo-Baena 
A(2), Espejo-Reina MJ(4).

Author information:
(1)Department of Orthopaedics, Hospital Virgen de la Victoria, Málaga, Spain.
