Developing a risk score to predict mortality in the first year after implantable 
cardioverter defibrillator implantation: Data from the Israeli ICD Registry.

Nevzorov R(1), Goldenberg I(2), Konstantino Y(3), Golovchiner G(4), Strasberg 
B(4), Souleiman M(5), Khalameizer V(1), Ben-Zvi S(6), Sela R(7), Rosenheck S(8), 
